, \"to\": 1656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke's is the 16th fastest globally this year.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stewart pointed out that Clarke, 20, has had his fair share of ups and downs with injuries this season, but he is now mentally ready to deliver an excellent performance at the showpiece in Paris.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.9949818032469944, \"rank\": 0.0050427641504658515, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\"}, {\"begin\": 1896, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996457518, \"rank\": 3.542788175345148e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"his fair share\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"ups\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"downs\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"an excellent performance\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"the showpiece\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you are pushing the throttle to get to the next level, you will always have little aches and pains here and there, but nothing to really worry about.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the throttle\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"the next level\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"little aches\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"pains\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we are well-oiled and greased at this time and getting better as the time counts down to the championships,\\\" Stewart pointed out.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.9949818032469944, \"rank\": 0.0050427641504658515, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"the championships\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained that the former Camperdown athlete, who is the World U-20 record holder in the event, has been working assiduously in training to improve all aspects of his hurdling technique in preparation for the Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2428, \"end\": 2433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996457518, \"rank\": 3.542788175345148e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the former Camperdown athlete\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"the World U-20 record holder\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"all aspects\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2361}, {\"ngram\": \"his hurdling technique\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2402}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stewart also highlighted that Clarke is very relaxed and focused at the moment, heading into the championships.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2435, \"end\": 2442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.9949818032469944, \"rank\": 0.0050427641504658515, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\": \"the championships\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We always plan to treat each race just like the next.\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each race\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We try not to put any pressure on ourselves, so the mental part is always to take it a step at a time and to treat each hurdle as it comes.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2742, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any pressure\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"the mental part\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"a step\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"each hurdle\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of the day, whatever we put out in training, we will be able to replicate in competition,\\\" Stewart maintains.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2845, \"end\": 2852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.9949818032469944, \"rank\": 0.0050427641504658515, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_Grand_Pr